description: Provides example URLs loaded by users in big orgs across varying percentiles.

schema.name: resource
schema.description: Stripped down name of the route minus org and query params.

schema.name: name
schema.description: The name of the user interaction performed, or 'route.load' if a Route Load.

schema.name: p50_url
schema.description: A recent example URL which experienced a p50 duration.

schema.name: p90_url
schema.description: A recent example URL which experienced a p90 duration.

schema.name: p95_url
schema.description: A recent example URL which experienced a p95 duration.

schema.name: p99_url
schema.description: A recent example URL which experienced a p99 duration.
